<br>
So this person pops a couple of bags worth of stuff in my window, including uber_sword01.  Also a centi short sword.  At this point I realize it's just a strange trader approach, so I figure I'll take a look.  So I ask about uber_sword01.  Trader responds with 'make an offer'.  Me, knowing my balance just isn't that high... I simply ask &quot;is it above the 2k range?&quot;<br>
<br>
Of course it is... <br>
<br>
*sighs*<br>
<br>
