<br>
It would have been easier had she simply used /auction....<br>
Instead both her and I wasted our time.  (I needed to meet someone else elsewhere and only stopped because of the &quot;I may have something for you&quot;...)<br>
<br>
How many folks use this approach?  And how many folks, like me, are annoyed at it? If I tell you &quot;I may have something for you&quot; .. I'm gonna give it to you as a present if it's an upgrade...<br>
